snippet.title: Karate Man Showcase - Heaven Studio
snippet.description:
EVERYTHING IN THIS VIDEO IS SUBJECT TO CHANGE

The Karate Man minigame has been entirely reworked from the ground up. Here's a showcase showing off some of the highlights!

Level created by @thatzeogal 

Download the level featured in the video: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1sVeauYxM-00X3I0wlfSgKnv89PeMnvV7/view?usp=sharing

GitHub  - https://github.com/RHeavenStudio/HeavenStudio
Discord - https://discord.gg/2kdZ8kFyEN
